### Ping — check X-Correlation-ID and X-Response-Time headers in response
GET http://localhost:7331/api/ping

### Ping with custom correlation ID
GET http://localhost:7331/api/ping
X-Correlation-ID: my-trace-123

### Internal endpoint — missing key (→ 401)
GET http://localhost:7331/api/internal

### Internal endpoint — with key (→ 200)
GET http://localhost:7331/api/internal
X-Internal-Key: dev-internal-key

### Health check
GET http://localhost:7331/health
